claim.claim-text:
61. The tool of claim 60, wherein said component controller is adapted to set a state of said nail firing mechanism as follows: 
if said orientation information indicates said nail firing mechanism is oriented in line with a location on said work piece where a nail is to be fired, 
said component controller enables said nail firing mechanism, and if said orientation information indicates said nail firing mechanism is not oriented in line with a location on said work piece where a nail is to be fired, said component controller disables said nail firing mechanism.
